    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>Render to an arbitrary number of displays by setting the <strong>Displays</strong> parameter to the desired number of displays. Each display can contain additional AOVs/LPE per display. We recommend OpenEXR and TIF formats. Note that we require OpenEXR for denoising.</p><h3 id=\"Output-DisplayOptions\">Display Options</h3><p>Display options become visible and editable when a display driver is selected. There are no additional options for interactive renders to the image tool or the Houdini display.</p><p /><p>Note that quantized 8-but images will default to sRGB output to avoid banding.</p><p /><p><strong>OpenEXR</strong></p><p>This is the preferred format for all of your renders. It provides an efficient format that holds your images, data, and more.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"911\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display0.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=704&amp;height=258\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645926/display0.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"258\" data-width=\"704\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645940\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"display0.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645926\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"36d17588-dfa3-4d05-810c-b27163cd088f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display0.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=704&amp;height=258 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display0.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=704&amp;height=258 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"911\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display1.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=703&amp;height=239\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645926/display1.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"239\" data-width=\"703\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645943\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"display1.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645926\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"be6c388c-d0a6-46d2-8e20-392c9868c5ba\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display1.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=703&amp;height=239 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display1.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=703&amp;height=239 1x\"></span><p>Bit depth is typically 16-float for color/illumination and 32-bit reserved for data like Z or Position</p><p>Zips compression is preferred by The Foundry's Nuke</p><p /><p><strong>TIF</strong></p><p>The common tif format is an older but still capable format for final renders</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"911\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display2.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=704&amp;height=281\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645926/display2.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"281\" data-width=\"704\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645946\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"display2.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645926\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"32983511-9700-4208-bd21-36aef14cfcaa\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display2.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=704&amp;height=281 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display2.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=704&amp;height=281 1x\"></span><p>Quantized renders are for non-float bit depth</p><p>Supported depth formats, float32 is preferred</p><p>The default compression choice of lzw is a common compression for most applications viewing Tiff files</p><p>The resolution unit is useful for conversion to print sizes</p><p /><p /><p><strong>PNG</strong></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"911\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display3.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147366&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=700&amp;height=211\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645926/display3.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147366&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"211\" data-width=\"700\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645949\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"display3.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645926\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3bcea3c9-0e1c-4459-9d1c-74fa890fa0d6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display3.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147366&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=700&amp;height=211 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display3.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147366&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=700&amp;height=211 1x\"></span><p /><p><strong>Targa</strong></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"913\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display4.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147367&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=703&amp;height=211\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645926/display4.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147367&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"211\" data-width=\"703\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645952\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"display4.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645926\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"96e0bfb0-d5cc-48a2-96e7-8df749dc6a8a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display4.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147367&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=703&amp;height=211 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display4.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147367&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=703&amp;height=211 1x\"></span><p /><p><strong>TEX (RenderMan Texture Format)</strong> We recommend Pixar Format for performance reasons.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"913\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display5.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147367&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=702&amp;height=357\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645926/display5.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147367&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"357\" data-width=\"702\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645955\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"display5.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645926\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b906b3ff-ab54-4cb8-a3a7-30b01b345106\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display5.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147367&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=702&amp;height=357 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645926/display5.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433147367&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=702&amp;height=357 1x\"></span><p>Render to a texture file, you can find more about these options in the <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661963\" rel=\"nofollow\">txmake</a> documentation.</p><p />"
    }
